item.description: ingredients 1/2 cups butter 1.5 cups sugar 1/2 cups vegetable oil 2 eggs 1 tsp vanilla 3 cups flour 1 tsp baking powder 1/2 tsp salt -------------------------- *optionals* 4 zested lemons instructions mix together like [[mag’s pound cake]] let dough set in fridge for minimum 3 hours bake in 350f oven for 10-15min until edges turn golden brown like a pound cake glaze with perfect icing or your favorite glaze recipe
